怎样我才能 进入那个迷宫啊？
How do I get into the labyrinth?

179
00:16:28,987 --> 00:16:32,582
这还差不多
Now that's more like it.

180
00:16:32,691 --> 00:16:35,524
你从这里进去
You gets in there.

181
00:16:44,603 --> 00:16:47,504
你真的要进去是吗？
You really going in there, are you?

182
00:16:49,741 --> 00:16:51,572
是的
Yes.

183
00:16:51,643 --> 00:16:54,168
恐怕我必须得去
I'm afraid I have to.

184
00:17:17,136 --> 00:17:18,763
挺容易是吗？
Cozy, isn't it?

185
00:17:24,042 --> 00:17:28,445
现在你是向左还是向右？
Now, would you go left or right?

186
00:17:30,949 --> 00:17:35,113
- 两面看起来都一样  - 嗯你不会走得太远的
- They both look the same. - Well, you're not gonna get very far.

187
00:17:35,187 --> 00:17:38,054
- 你会去哪边？  - 我？
- Which way would you go? - Me?

188
00:17:38,157 --> 00:17:39,624
两面我都不去
I wouldn't go either way.

189
00:17:39,691 --> 00:17:42,455
如果你只愿意帮忙到这里的话 你可以走了
If that's all the help you're gonna be, you can just leave.

190
00:17:42,561 --> 00:17:46,691
你知道你的问题在哪吗？ 你得自己努力
You know your problem? You take too many things for granted.

191
00:17:47,599 --> 00:17:49,123
拿这个迷宫来说
Take this labyrinth...

192
00:17:49,201 --> 00:17:52,432
即使你到了它的中间 你也走不出来
Even if you get to the center, you'll never get out again.

193
00:17:52,504 --> 00:17:56,531
- 那是你的看法  - 至少比你的好
- That's your opinion. - It's a lot better than yours.

194
00:17:57,709 --> 00:17:59,973
就算这样也多谢你 霍格特
Thanks for nothing, Hogwart.

195
00:18:01,380 --> 00:18:05,214
是霍格 别说我没警告你
It's Hoggle! And don't say I didn't warn you.

196
00:19:09,681 --> 00:19:12,707
什么“迷宫”啊？ 没有拐弯也没有拐角
What do they mean, "labyrinth"? There aren't any turns or corners.

197
00:19:12,784 --> 00:19:15,150
只是不断延伸下去
It just goes on and on.

198
00:19:21,960 --> 00:19:23,894
或许它有尽头
Maybe it doesn't.

199
00:19:25,597 --> 00:19:28,828
或许只是我以为它有没有
Maybe I'm just taking it for granted that it does.

200
00:20:17,949 --> 00:20:19,382
您好
'Allo.

201
00:20:27,326 --> 00:20:28,691
是你说“哈喽”的吗？
Did you say "hello"?

202
00:20:28,760 --> 00:20:31,456
不 我是说“啊喽” 不过也差不多了
No, I said "'allo," but that's close enough.

203
00:20:33,632 --> 00:20:37,090
- 你是只蠕虫是吗？  - 没错
- You're a worm, aren't you? - That's right.

204
00:20:37,169 --> 00:20:40,195
或许你知道怎样通过这个迷宫吧？
You don't by any chance know the way through this labyrinth?

205
00:20:40,272 --> 00:20:42,763
谁 我？我我只是条虫子
Who, me? No, I'm just a worm.

206
00:20:44,643 --> 00:20:46,440
进来见见我太太吧
Come inside, meet the missus.

207
00:20:46,545 --> 00:20:50,709
不谢谢你 我先得搞定这个迷宫
No, thank you, but I have to solve this labyrinth.

208
00:20:50,782 --> 00:20:53,410
可是这条巷即没有拐弯又没有出口 什么都没有
But there aren't any turns or any openings or anything.

209
00:20:53,485 --> 00:20:55,578
一望又没有尽头
It just goes on and on.

210
00:20:55,654 --> 00:20:59,556
你只是看不到 这里到处都是出口 但你却看不见
You ain't looking right. It's full of openings, but you ain't seeing 'em.

211
00:20:59,658 --> 00:21:01,990
- 出口在哪？  - 穿过那儿就有一个
- Where are they? - There's one just across there.

212
00:21:02,060 --> 00:21:04,426
就在你前面
It's right in front of ya.

213
00:21:05,497 --> 00:21:06,623
没有啊
No, there isn't.

214
00:21:06,698 --> 00:21:09,496
进来喝杯茶吧
Come inside and have a nice cup of tea.

215
00:21:09,568 --> 00:21:13,561
- 但这里没有出口啊  - 肯定有
- But there isn't an opening. - Of course there is.

216
00:21:13,672 --> 00:21:17,199
你试着走过去 你就明白我的意思了
You try walking through it. You'll see what I mean.

217
00:21:17,275 --> 00:21:18,367
什么？
What?

218
00:21:18,477 --> 00:21:19,944
继续
Go on then.

219
00:21:22,080 --> 00:21:25,072
那只是一堵墙 没有进去的路啊
That's just wall. There's no way through.

220
00:21:25,117 --> 00:21:27,415
这里的东西并不总跟你所看到的一样
Things are not always what they seem in this place.

221
00:21:27,486 --> 00:21:30,944
所以你不能光看表面
So you can't take anything for granted.

222
00:21:38,096 --> 00:21:39,495
嘿
Hey!

223
00:21:40,799 --> 00:21:42,960
- 继续  - 谢谢你
- Hang on. - Thank you.

224
00:21:43,034 --> 00:21:46,162
- 您真帮了我的大忙  - 别去那边
- That was incredibly helpful. - Don't go that way.

225
00:21:46,238 --> 00:21:49,036
- 什么？  - 我说别去那边
- What was that? - I said, don't go that way.

226
00:21:49,107 --> 00:21:51,769
绝对不要走这条路
Never go that way.

227
00:21:51,843 --> 00:21:54,710
噢多谢
Oh. Thanks.

228
00:21:54,813 --> 00:21:57,976
如果她坚持走那条路的话…
If she had kept on going down that way...

229
00:21:58,049 --> 00:22:00,882
那她很快就会到城堡了
she'd had gone straight to that castle.

230
00:22:11,329 --> 00:22:12,626
托比
Toby.

231
00:22:14,733 --> 00:22:16,633
我来啦 托比
I'm coming, Toby.

232
00:22:27,946 --> 00:22:31,006
把这个还给我 快点 离我远点
Give me back this! Go on, get off me.

233
00:22:31,950 --> 00:22:34,248
别走这条路 你在说什么？
Stay out of the way. What are you talking about?

234
00:22:34,352 --> 00:22:36,252
走走走
Walk, walk, walk.

235
00:23:00,078 --> 00:23:02,069
- 你让我想起了小孩  - 什么小孩？
- You remind me of the babe. - What babe?

236
00:23:02,113 --> 00:23:03,671
- 拥有魔法的小孩  - 什么魔法？
- The babe with the power. - What power?

237
00:23:03,782 --> 00:23:05,340
-  伏都魔法  - 谁会魔法？
- The power of voodoo. - Who do?

238
00:23:05,417 --> 00:23:06,475
- 你会  - 会什么？
- You do. - Do what?

239
00:23:06,585 --> 00:23:09,315
让我想起了小孩
Remind me of the babe.

240
00:23:09,387 --> 00:23:12,015
安静点 一个小妖精
Quiet! A goblin babe.

241
00:23:15,894 --> 00:23:17,293
嗯？
Well?

242
00:23:17,650 --> 00:23:20,594
DAVID BOWIE - DANCE MAGIC

243
00:24:28,567 --> 00:24:30,501
嘿 出了什么事吗？
Hey, what goes on?

244
00:24:35,874 --> 00:24:38,866
你妈妈是个土豚
Your mother is an aardvark!

245
00:24:56,928 --> 00:24:59,795
9个小时零23分钟后…
In 9 hours and 23 minutes...

246
00:24:59,898 --> 00:25:01,798
你就是我的了
you'll be mine.

247
00:26:33,491 --> 00:26:34,788
- 你明白了吗？  - 我明白了
- You got it? - I got it.

248
00:26:34,893 --> 00:26:37,327
- 不错  - 嘘
- Good. - Shh!

249
00:26:48,907 --> 00:26:52,035
有人改了我的标记
Someone has been changing my marks.

250
00:26:52,110 --> 00:26:55,307
这真是个可怕的地方 这不公平
What a horrible place this is. It's not fair!

251
00:26:55,413 --> 00:26:57,938
你说的对 这不公平
That's right. It's not fair.

252
00:26:59,417 --> 00:27:01,146
而这只是其中一部分
But that's only half of it.

253
00:27:02,520 --> 00:27:06,786
- 一分钟之前这里还是个死胡同  - 不 在你后面的才是死胡同
- This was a dead end a minute ago. - No, that's the dead end behind you.

254
00:27:11,830 --> 00:27:14,560
它总是在变 我该怎么办呢？
It keeps changing. What am I supposed to do?

255
00:27:14,632 --> 00:27:17,624
唯一的出路 就在这其中的一个门
The only way out of here is to try one of these doors.

256
00:27:17,736 --> 00:27:20,637
其中一个通向迷宫中间的城堡
One of them leads to the castle at the center of the labyrinth.

257
00:27:20,672 --> 00:27:23,038
- 另一个通向…  - 哺哺哺哺
- And the other one leads to... - Boom-boom-ba-boom.

258
00:27:23,141 --> 00:27:25,041
死亡
Certain death.

259
00:27:28,146 --> 00:27:30,706
哪个是哪个？
Which one is which?

260
00:27:30,782 --> 00:27:32,807
- 我们不能告诉你  - 为什么不能？
- We can't tell you. - Why not?

261
00:27:35,253 --> 00:27:37,551
- 我们不知道  - 但就是这样
- We don't know. - But they do.

262
00:27:37,655 --> 00:27:39,589
哦 那我就去问他们
Oh. Then I'll ask them.

263
00:27:41,359 --> 00:27:44,658
不 你不能问我们俩 你只能问我们其中一个
No, you can't ask us. You can only ask one of us.

264
00:27:44,763 --> 00:27:47,664
这是规则 而且我得警告你…
It's in the rules, and I should warn you...

265
00:27:47,699 --> 00:27:49,428
我们其中一人总是说实话…
one of us always tells the truth...

266
00:27:49,501 --> 00:27:51,662
而另一人总是说慌
and one of us always lies.

267
00:27:51,770 --> 00:27:54,204
这也是规则 他总是说谎
That's a rule too. He always lies.

268
00:27:54,272 --> 00:27:57,764
- 我没有 我讲的是实话  - 哦 你看这谎说的
- I do not. I tell the truth. - Oh, what a lie.

269
00:28:00,078 --> 00:28:01,306
他说谎
He's the liar.

270
00:28:02,080 --> 00:28:04,071
好吧 回答是或不是
All right. Answer yes or no.

271
00:28:05,383 --> 00:28:09,080
他会告诉我这扇门是通向城堡的吗？
Would he tell me that this door leads to the castle?

272
00:28:13,431 --> 00:28:15,766
- 你认为呢？  - 我不知道
-What do you think? -l don't know.

273
00:28:15,894 --> 00:28:16,986
是的
Yes.

274
00:28:17,829 --> 00:28:20,992
那么另一扇门通向城堡…
Then the other door leads to the castle...

275
00:28:21,099 --> 00:28:22,999
而这扇门通向死亡
and this door leads to certain death.

276
00:28:23,101 --> 00:28:25,763
- 噢！  - 你怎么知道？
- Ooh! - How do you know?

277
00:28:25,837 --> 00:28:28,704
- 他可能在说实话  - 那么你却不会
- He could be telling the truth. - But then you wouldn't be.

278
00:28:28,807 --> 00:28:31,469
因此如果你告诉我他说是 我就知道答案是不
So if you told me that he said yes, I know the answer is no.

279
00:28:31,543 --> 00:28:34,376
- 但我也可能在说实话  - 那么他说谎也行啊
- But I could be telling the truth. - But then he would be lying.

280
00:28:34,445 --> 00:28:37,903
如果你告诉我他说是 我知道答案仍然是否
So if you told me that he said yes, I know the answer would still be no.

281
00:28:38,016 --> 00:28:40,075
等一等 是这样吗？
Wait a minute. Is that right?

282
00:28:40,151 --> 00:28:42,779
我不知道 我搞不清楚
I don't know. I've never understood it.

283
00:28:44,122 --> 00:28:47,216
就是这样 我想出来了
No, it's right. I figured it out.

284
00:28:47,325 --> 00:28:49,452
以前我就想不出来
I could never do it before.

285
00:28:49,527 --> 00:28:53,486
我想我越来越聪明了 这是小菜一碟
I think I'm getting smarter. This is a piece of cake.

286
00:28:56,734 --> 00:28:58,167
救命啊！
Help!

287
00:29:01,539 --> 00:29:03,234
不要这样！救命啊！
Stop it! Help!

288
00:29:04,075 --> 00:29:07,044
你不是喊救命吗？ 我们正在救你
What do you mean, "help"? We are helping.

289
00:29:07,145 --> 00:29:09,113
我们是救命手
We're helping hands.

290
00:29:09,180 --> 00:29:10,807
你们弄痛我了
You're hurting.

291
00:29:10,882 --> 00:29:13,646
你要我们放手吗？
Would you like us to let go?

292
00:29:15,189 --> 00:29:16,940
不
No!

293
00:29:16,988 --> 00:29:19,320
那好 哪一边？
Well, then come on, which way?

294
00:29:19,390 --> 00:29:20,789
哪一边？
Which way?

295
00:29:20,859 --> 00:29:23,623
上还是下？
Up or down?

296
00:29:23,695 --> 00:29:26,220
- 噢  - 说啊 说啊
- Oh. - Come on, come on.

297
00:29:26,297 --> 00:29:28,265
我们没时间磨蹭
We haven't got all day.

298
00:29:28,299 --> 00:29:31,097
看来这个决定很重大
Well, it's a big decision for her.

299
00:29:31,169 --> 00:29:34,161
你想去哪一边啊？
Which way do you want to go, hmm?

300
00:29:35,206 --> 00:29:36,537
是啊 哪一边？
Yes, which way?

301
00:29:38,076 --> 00:29:41,409
既然我在向下 那就下吧
Well, since I'm pointed that way, I guess I'll go down.

302
00:29:41,479 --> 00:29:44,539
她选择下
She chose down.

303
00:29:44,616 --> 00:29:46,811
她选择下？
She chose down?

304
00:29:46,885 --> 00:29:49,786
- 错了吗？  - 太迟了
- Was that wrong? - Too late now.

305
00:30:03,501 --> 00:30:05,799
她掉进了地牢
She's in the oubliette.

306
00:30:05,904 --> 00:30:08,930
住口！她不应该来到地牢
Shut up! She should not have gotten as far as the oubliette.

307
00:30:09,007 --> 00:30:12,408
- 她现在应该放弃了  - 她不会放弃的
- She should have given up by now. - She'll never give up.

308
00:30:12,510 --> 00:30:15,707
不会吗？ 矮子会带她回到入口处
Won't she? The dwarf's about to lead her back to the beginning.

309
00:30:15,813 --> 00:30:20,273
当她意识到要从头开始 就会马上放弃
She'll soon give up when she realizes she has to start all over again.

310
00:30:21,920 --> 00:30:23,319
那么笑吧
Well, laugh.

311
00:30:33,064 --> 00:30:34,497
是谁？
Who's there?

312
00:30:34,565 --> 00:30:35,998
是我
Me.

313
00:30:37,368 --> 00:30:39,996
- 噢是你  - 嗯是的…
- Oh, it's you. - Oh, yes, well...

314
00:30:40,071 --> 00:30:43,131
我一见到你 就知道你将会有麻烦…
I knew you were gonna get into trouble as soon as I met you...

315
00:30:43,241 --> 00:30:45,675
所以我来帮你了
so I've come to give you a hand.

316
00:30:47,045 --> 00:30:49,172
你在到处看呢 不是吗？
Oh, you're looking around now, aren't you?

317
00:30:49,247 --> 00:30:52,080
我想你应该发现这里没有门
I suppose you noticed there ain't no doors.

318
00:30:52,150 --> 00:30:54,084
只有那个洞口
Only the hole.

319
00:30:55,386 --> 00:30:58,617
这是一间地牢 迷宫里到处都是
This is an oubliette. The labyrinth's full of them.

320
00:30:58,690 --> 00:31:01,784
- 真的？你怎么知道的？  - 噢 真笨
- Really? How do you know that? - Oh, don't sound so smart.

321
00:31:01,859 --> 00:31:05,124
- 你不知道地牢是什么  - 你知道吗？
- You don't know what an oubliette is. - Do you?

322
00:31:05,196 --> 00:31:08,222
当然那是你把别人关起来…
Yes, it's a place you put people...

323
00:31:08,299 --> 00:31:10,426
让他们忘记自己的地方
to forget about 'em.

324
00:31:10,501 --> 00:31:14,130
现在你要做的 就是离开这里
Now, what you've gotta do is get out of here.

325
00:31:14,205 --> 00:31:17,174
碰巧我知道一条捷径…
And it so happens that I know a short cut...

326
00:31:17,208 --> 00:31:19,301
能够离开迷宫
out of the whole labyrinth from here.

327
00:31:19,377 --> 00:31:21,572
不 我现在不打算放弃
No, I'm not giving up now.

328
00:31:21,679 --> 00:31:23,579
我都走这么远了
I've come too far.

329
00:31:27,485 --> 00:31:31,285
- 我很好  - 你当然很好
- No, I'm doing okay. - Of course you are.

330
00:31:31,389 --> 00:31:34,552
但是被困在这里就不好了
But it gets a lot worse from here on in.

331
00:31:36,027 --> 00:31:38,359
你为什么这么关心我？
Why are you so concerned about me?

332
00:31:38,429 --> 00:31:41,330
哦 我就是这样的
Well, I am, that's all.

333
00:31:41,399 --> 00:31:45,859
不想看到这么年轻漂亮的女孩 被困在又黑又恐怖的地牢里
Nice, young girl. Terrible, black oubliette.

334
00:31:46,904 --> 00:31:49,270
你喜欢珠宝 对吗？
You like jewelry, don't you?

335
00:31:49,340 --> 00:31:50,967
干嘛？
Why?

336
00:31:51,042 --> 00:31:54,910
如果你帮我走出迷宫 我给你这个
If you help me solve the labyrinth, I'll give you this.

337
00:31:57,648 --> 00:31:59,707
你很喜欢 是吗？
You like it, don't you?

338
00:31:59,817 --> 00:32:02,877
- 一般般  - 那好
- So-so. - Oh. Okay.

339
00:32:04,722 --> 00:32:07,520
这样吧 你把手镯给我…
Tell you what... you give me the bracelet...

340
00:32:07,625 --> 00:32:09,525
我就带你离开迷宫
and I'll show you the way out of the labyrinth.

341
00:32:09,627 --> 00:32:12,255
- 你一定要这么做  - 是的
- You were gonna do that anyway. - Yes.

342
00:32:12,330 --> 00:32:16,733
这样做是对你示好的姿态
That's what would make it a particularly nice gesture on your part.

343
00:32:16,768 --> 00:32:18,531
这样吧…
I'll tell you what...

344
00:32:18,636 --> 00:32:21,400
如果你不带我去迷宫中心 尽量把我带近一些
if you won't take me to the center, take me as far as you can.

345
00:32:21,472 --> 00:32:24,839
- 然后我自己走  - 这是什么做的？
- Then I'll do it on my own. - What is that anyway?

346
00:32:26,044 --> 00:32:27,136
塑料
Plastic.

347
00:32:29,447 --> 00:32:32,473
那么我答应你…
I don't promise nothing, but...

348
00:32:32,550 --> 00:32:36,509
我尽量把你带近些 然后你自己走 是吗？
I'll take you as far as I can, then you're on your own, right?

349
00:32:36,587 --> 00:32:38,748
- 是  - 那好
- Right. - Right.

350
00:32:40,091 --> 00:32:42,059
喔 塑料的！
Wow. Plastic!

351
00:32:46,497 --> 00:32:48,465
走吧
Here we go.

352
00:32:54,072 --> 00:32:55,699
该死的
Damn.

353
00:32:55,773 --> 00:32:57,206
垃圾房
Broom closet.

354
00:32:59,477 --> 00:33:02,378
不是每一次都灵
Well, can't be right all the time.

355
00:33:05,483 --> 00:33:08,475
对了 来吧
This is it. Come on then.

356
00:33:15,827 --> 00:33:19,092
- 这边  - 不要往前走了- This way. - Don't go on.

357
00:33:19,197 --> 00:33:22,462
趁你还有机会 赶快回去吧
Go back while you still can.

358
00:33:22,533 --> 00:33:25,696
这条路不对
This is not the way.

359
00:33:25,803 --> 00:33:29,295
当心 不要再向前了
Take heed and go no further.

360
00:33:29,407 --> 00:33:33,707
小心 小心
Beware. Beware.

361
00:33:33,744 --> 00:33:36,212
就快来不及了
Soon it will be too late.

362
00:33:36,314 --> 00:33:38,578
唉！别理它们
Yeah! Don't pay any attention to them.

363
00:33:38,649 --> 00:33:42,210
它们是假警报 在迷宫到处都可以看到
They're just false alarms. You get a lot of them in the labyrinth.

364
00:33:42,320 --> 00:33:44,288
特别是当你走对路时
Especially when you're on the right track.

365
00:33:44,355 --> 00:33:47,324
- 不 你走错路了  - 住口
- Oh, no, you're not. - Oh, shut up.

366
00:33:47,358 --> 00:33:50,555
- 对不起 我只是在工作  - 没必要对我们说
- Sorry. Just doing my job. - You don't have to do it to us.

367
00:33:50,628 --> 00:33:53,654
- 当心了  - 得了
- Beware for... - Just forget it.

368
00:33:53,731 --> 00:33:57,394
让我说吧 我很久没说话了
Oh, please, I haven't said it for such a long time.

369
00:33:57,468 --> 00:34:00,960
也好 不过别指望我们会有多大的反应
Oh, all right, but don't expect a big reaction.

370
00:34:01,038 --> 00:34:03,768
不不不 当然不会
No, no, no, of course not.

371
00:34:03,841 --> 00:34:07,971
你们正在走向毁灭
For the path you will take will lead to certain destruction.

372
00:34:09,046 --> 00:34:10,980
- 太谢谢你了  - 噢
- Thank you very much. - Uh-oh.

373
00:34:11,048 --> 00:34:12,174
噢 不好
Oh, no.

374
00:34:18,389 --> 00:34:20,482
我们碰到什么了？
What have we here?

375
00:34:20,558 --> 00:34:22,890
- 没什么  - 没什么？
- Nothing. - Nothing?

376
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:25,690
没什么？没什么？
Nothing? Nothing?

377
00:34:25,763 --> 00:34:27,697
没什么 哇啦啦
Nothing, tra-la-la.

378
00:34:27,765 --> 00:34:30,757
国王陛下 见到你太意外了
Your Majesty, what a nice surprise.

379
00:34:30,868 --> 00:34:32,995
- 你好 霍特沃得  - 霍格特
- Hello, Hedgewart. - Hogwart.

380
00:34:33,070 --> 00:34:34,503
霍格！
Hoggle!

381
00:34:34,572 --> 00:34:37,473
霍格 你在帮助这个女孩吗？
Hoggle, can it be that you're helping this girl?

382
00:34:37,508 --> 00:34:40,375
帮助？这是什么话？
Helping? In what sense?

383
00:34:40,478 --> 00:34:42,912
我是说你正在带她到城堡
In the sense that you're leading her towards the castle.

384
00:34:42,980 --> 00:34:46,245
不我在带她到入口处 国王陛下
No, I was taking her back to the beginning, Your Majesty.

385
00:34:46,317 --> 00:34:47,750
什么？
What?

386
00:34:47,818 --> 00:34:51,310
我告诉她 我会帮她走进迷宫
I told her I was going to help her solve the labyrinth.

387
00:34:51,389 --> 00:34:54,586
我在骗她 实际上…
A little trickery on my part. But actually...

388
00:34:54,692 --> 00:34:57,718
你手腕上的塑料是什么？
What is that plastic thing 'round your wrist?

389
00:35:00,331 --> 00:35:01,593
噢 这个！
Oh, this!

390
00:35:03,834 --> 00:35:06,394
天哪 这是哪来的？
My goodness, where did this come from?

391
00:35:06,504 --> 00:35:07,994
- 希格…  - 霍格
- Higgle... - Hoggle.

392
00:35:08,105 --> 00:35:10,801
如果我知道你在背叛我…
If I thought for one second that you were betraying me...

393
00:35:10,908 --> 00:35:14,844
我就不得不把你倒挂在永久恶臭的沼泽上
I'd be forced to suspend you headfirst in the Bog of Eternal Stench.

394
00:35:14,912 --> 00:35:19,008
不要 国王陛下！ 不要那里！
No, Your Majesty! Not the Eternal Stench!

395
00:35:19,116 --> 00:35:21,016
怕了吗 霍格！
Oh, yes, Hoggle!

396
00:35:21,118 --> 00:35:23,609
你呢 莎拉
And you, Sarah.

397
00:35:23,721 --> 00:35:25,689
觉得我的迷宫怎样？
How are you enjoying my labyrinth?

398
00:35:28,059 --> 00:35:30,027
小菜一碟
It's a piece of cake.

399
00:35:30,061 --> 00:35:31,722
噢！
Oh!

400
00:35:31,829 --> 00:35:35,128
真的？那么 把时间拨快点把？
Really? Then how about upping the stakes?

401
00:35:35,233 --> 00:35:37,531
哼？
Hmm?

402
00:35:37,635 --> 00:35:39,159
这不公平！
That's not fair!

403
00:35:39,237 --> 00:35:41,330
你说很多次了
You say that so often.

404
00:35:41,439 --> 00:35:45,273
我想知道你和什么比较
I wonder what your basis for comparison is.

405
00:35:45,343 --> 00:35:47,834
迷宫是小菜一碟 是吗？
So the labyrinth's a piece of cake, is it?

406
00:35:47,878 --> 00:35:51,370
那么看看你怎么对付这个小玩意
Well, let's see how you deal with this little slice.

407
00:35:58,856 --> 00:36:01,154
噢不 是扫除机！
Oh, no, the cleaners!

408
00:36:01,259 --> 00:36:03,159
- 什么？  - 快跑！
- What? - Run!

409
00:36:09,567 --> 00:36:11,330
你还好吧？
You okay?

410
00:36:13,904 --> 00:36:15,337
来吧！
Come on!

411
00:36:16,774 --> 00:36:18,173
快点！
Faster!

412
00:36:25,616 --> 00:36:27,777
扫除机！恶臭沼泽！
The cleaners! The Bog of Stench!

413
00:36:27,885 --> 00:36:30,479
你让他认真起来了
You sure got his attention.

414
00:36:53,544 --> 00:36:56,604
啊 这正是我们要的
Ah, this is what we need.

415
00:36:56,714 --> 00:36:58,944
一个梯子 来吧
A ladder. Follow me.

416
00:36:59,016 --> 00:37:02,679
你刚才想把我带回入口处 我现在如何相信你？
How can I trust you now that I know you were taking me back to the beginning?

417
00:37:02,753 --> 00:37:04,311
我没有
I wasn't.

418
00:37:04,422 --> 00:37:08,825
我告诉他我在带你回入口处 是为了分散他的注意
I told him I was taking you back to the beginning to throw him off the scent.

419
00:37:08,926 --> 00:37:11,690
霍格，我如何相信你的话呢？
Hoggle, how can I believe anything you say?

420
00:37:11,762 --> 00:37:14,560
好吧 这么说吧
Well, let me put it this way.

421
00:37:14,632 --> 00:37:16,759
你还有什么选择呢？
What choice have you got?

422
00:37:19,136 --> 00:37:20,569
那倒是
You're right.

423
00:37:23,140 --> 00:37:26,371
看来你开始了解我的处境了
You see, you've gotta understand my position.

424
00:37:26,444 --> 00:37:29,936
我是胆小鬼 佳拉斯吓倒我了
I'm a coward, and Jareth scares me.

425
00:37:30,047 --> 00:37:34,108
- 什么样的处境？  - 没地位 我认为
- What kind of position is that? - No position. That's my point.

426
00:37:34,185 --> 00:37:37,177
如果你闻过永久恶臭的沼泽…
You wouldn't be so brave if you'd ever smelled...

427
00:37:37,254 --> 00:37:39,347
你就不会这么勇敢了
the Bog of Eternal Stench.

428
00:37:39,457 --> 00:37:41,482
那是…那是…
It's... It's...

429
00:37:44,662 --> 00:37:46,755
真的很臭吗？
Is that all it does, is smell?

430
00:37:46,864 --> 00:37:49,162
相信我 是真的
Believe me, that's enough.

431
00:37:49,266 --> 00:37:51,962
更糟糕的是 万一你不幸…
But the worst thing is, if you so much...

432
00:37:52,069 --> 00:37:54,128
把脚踏进恶臭沼泽…
as put a foot in the Bog of Stench...

433
00:37:54,205 --> 00:37:57,436
你的余生都会很臭
you'll smell bad for the rest of your life.

434
00:37:57,508 --> 00:38:00,136
洗不掉的
It'll never wash off.

435
00:38:04,382 --> 00:38:08,011
我们到了 从现在起你要靠自己了
Here we are then. You're on your own from now on.

436
00:38:09,186 --> 00:38:12,678
- 什么？  - 到此为止 我走了
- What? - That's it. I quit.

437
00:38:12,790 --> 00:38:14,690
等一等
Wait a minute.

438
00:38:17,695 --> 00:38:21,688
我遵守诺言了 我说过我能带多远就多远
I didn't promise nothin'. I said I'd take you as far as I could go.

439
00:38:21,799 --> 00:38:24,529
你这个小骗子 你无耻
You little cheat. You nasty little cheat.

440
00:38:24,602 --> 00:38:27,537
别为难我了 我没有自尊
Don't try to embarrass me. I've got no pride.

441
00:38:27,605 --> 00:38:29,664
真的？
Oh, yeah?

442
00:38:29,740 --> 00:38:31,435
这是我的珠宝！
But them's my jewels!

443
00:38:31,509 --> 00:38:34,967
还给我 还给我 把它们还给我
You give 'em back. Give them back. Give those back.

444
00:38:36,514 --> 00:38:38,243
把它们还给我！
Give those back to me!

445
00:38:38,315 --> 00:38:42,809
现在城堡就在那边 我们该走哪边呢？
Now, there's the castle. Which way should we try?

446
00:38:42,920 --> 00:38:46,947
那是我的财产 这不公平！
Them's my rightful property. It's not fair!

447
00:38:47,024 --> 00:38:49,515
就是不公平的
No, it isn't.

448
00:38:49,560 --> 00:38:51,960
事实就是这样
But that's the way it is.

449
00:39:00,638 --> 00:39:04,039
不好意思 你能帮帮我吗？
Excuse me, please, but can you help me?

450
00:39:04,141 --> 00:39:06,302
噢 小女孩！
Oh, a young girl!

451
00:39:09,046 --> 00:39:11,412
他是谁？
And who is this?

452
00:39:12,349 --> 00:39:15,284
- 我朋友  - 是啊
- My friend. - Oh, yes.

453
00:39:15,352 --> 00:39:17,843
有什么能帮你？
And what can I do for you?

454
00:39:17,955 --> 00:39:20,014
麻烦你告诉我… 就是…
Please, can you tell... That is...

455
00:39:20,090 --> 00:39:22,615
我要去迷宫中央的城堡
I have to get to the castle at the center of the labyrinth.

456
00:39:22,693 --> 00:39:24,661
你知道该怎么走吗？
Do you know the way?

457
00:39:26,363 --> 00:39:28,923
那么
Well, yes, now.

458
00:39:28,999 --> 00:39:31,661
你想要去城堡
You want to get to the castle.

459
00:39:31,769 --> 00:39:34,033
脑筋不是很好啊？
How's that for brain power, huh?

460
00:39:34,104 --> 00:39:35,401
安静！
Be quiet!

461
00:39:35,473 --> 00:39:37,236
啊 生气了
Ah, nuts.

462
00:39:37,308 --> 00:39:40,368
那么 小姐…
So, young woman...

463
00:39:40,478 --> 00:39:44,812
向前的路有时是往回的
the way forward is sometimes the way back.

464
00:39:46,817 --> 00:39:49,615
你会听这个废物的话吗！
Will you listen to this crap!

465
00:39:49,687 --> 00:39:52,850
- 你静一点好吗！  - 好 对不起
- Will you please be quiet! - Sorry. All right.

466
00:39:52,923 --> 00:39:54,049
- 好吗  - 好！
- Okay. - Okay!

467
00:39:54,124 --> 00:39:56,183
- 好吗  - 好！
- All right. - All right!

468
00:39:56,293 --> 00:39:58,193
- 什么？  - 对不起
- What? - Sorry.

469
00:40:00,231 --> 00:40:01,664
说完了吗？
Finished?

470
00:40:02,900 --> 00:40:04,299
是
Yes.

471
00:40:05,436 --> 00:40:08,132
小姐 很多时候…
Quite often, young lady...

472
00:40:08,205 --> 00:40:12,608
看起来我们哪里也去不了 但是事实上…
it seems like we're not getting anywhere, when in fact...

473
00:40:12,710 --> 00:40:16,043
- 我们确实在前进  - 是的
- We are. - We are.

474
00:40:16,113 --> 00:40:19,412
我现在当然哪儿也去不了
I'm certainly not getting anywhere at the moment.

475
00:40:19,517 --> 00:40:20,711
加入俱乐部吧
Join the club.

476
00:40:24,555 --> 00:40:27,683
我想这是你的命运
I think that's your lot.

477
00:40:27,758 --> 00:40:30,989
请在这个小盒子里 捐献点什么吧
Please leave a contribution in the little box.

478
00:40:33,030 --> 00:40:35,055
你敢！那是我的
Don't you dare! Them's mine.

479
00:40:39,670 --> 00:40:42,662
我想我可以捐出这个
Well, I guess I can spare this.

480
00:40:47,945 --> 00:40:50,937
你没有必要把那个给他
Oh, you didn't have to give him that.

481
00:40:50,981 --> 00:40:52,949
他告诉你一些事情了
He didn't tell you nothin'.

482
00:40:52,983 --> 00:40:56,180
好了 两个蠢材上当了
Well, then. There go a couple of suckers.

483
00:40:58,589 --> 00:41:01,615
啊 当你的帽子真刺激
Ah, it's so stimulating being your hat.

484
00:41:03,761 --> 00:41:05,922
为什么…为什么你那么说…
Why... Why did you say that...

485
00:41:05,996 --> 00:41:08,123
说我是你的朋友？
about my being your friend?

486
00:41:08,198 --> 00:41:09,688
因为你就是我的朋友
Because you are.

487
00:41:09,767 --> 00:41:12,861
你可能不是我真正的朋友 但在这里你是我唯一的朋友
You may not be much of a friend, but you're the only one I've got here.

488
00:41:14,405 --> 00:41:16,635
你听到什么吗？
Do you hear something?

489
00:41:16,707 --> 00:41:19,175
- 没有 一切正常  - 朋友
- No, it's all right. - Friend.

490
00:41:20,611 --> 00:41:21,873
我喜欢这样
I like that.

491
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:25,781
以前我从来没有朋友
I ain't never been no one's friend before.

492
00:41:27,718 --> 00:41:30,084
- 再见！  - 等一等
- Good-bye! - Wait a minute.

493
00:41:30,187 --> 00:41:32,155
- 留着我的东西  - 你是不是我的朋友？
- Keep the stuff. - Are you my friend or not?

494
00:41:32,222 --> 00:41:34,622
不 我不是 霍格没有朋友
No, I'm not. Hoggle ain't no one's friend.

495
00:41:34,692 --> 00:41:37,684
他照顾他自己 跟其他人一样
He looks after himself, like everyone.

496
00:41:37,728 --> 00:41:40,492
霍格的朋友就是他自己
Hoggle is Hoggle's friend.

497
00:41:40,598 --> 00:41:43,089
霍格 你这个胆小鬼！
Hoggle, you coward!

498
00:41:46,003 --> 00:41:47,903
我才不怕
Well, I'm not afraid.

499
00:41:48,005 --> 00:41:51,338
在这里经常眼见不为实
Things aren't always what they seem in this place.

500
00:41:57,648 --> 00:42:00,811
试试这个吧 大雪人！
Try on this for size, you big yeti!

501
00:42:00,918 --> 00:42:03,512
我们抓到你了 怪物！
We've got you now, fuzz ball!

502
00:42:04,922 --> 00:42:06,219
一起来吧
All together now.

503
00:42:13,464 --> 00:42:16,297
要是我有东西 扔过去就好了
If only I had something to throw.

504
00:42:24,541 --> 00:42:26,532
咬他！咬他！
Sock it to him! Sock it to him!

505
00:42:30,280 --> 00:42:34,944
怎么回事？谁关灯？ 我看不见！
What happened? Who turned out the light? I can't see!

506
00:42:36,687 --> 00:42:39,747
- 你干嘛咬我？  - 谁咬谁？
- Why'd you bite me? - Who bite who?

507
00:42:39,857 --> 00:42:42,155
谁咬我？谁咬我？
Who bite me? Who bite me?

508
00:42:43,494 --> 00:42:46,258
- 我看不见！  - 发生什么事？
- I can't see! - What is going on?

509
00:42:50,200 --> 00:42:53,101
撤退！
Retreat!

510
00:42:55,072 --> 00:42:56,198
谁咬我？
Who bit me?

511
00:42:56,273 --> 00:42:58,707
噢 我心爱的生鱼片！
Oh, my aching sushi!

512
00:43:11,288 --> 00:43:13,188
停止
Now, stop that.

513
00:43:15,492 --> 00:43:18,052
你就这样对待救你的人的吗？
Is that any way to treat someone who's trying to help you?

514
00:43:19,229 --> 00:43:22,096
你要我放你下来吗？
Don't you want me to help you down?

515
00:43:23,534 --> 00:43:27,994
放下鲁德
Ludo down.

516
00:43:28,038 --> 00:43:29,471
鲁德？
Ludo?

517
00:43:30,641 --> 00:43:31,733
是你的名字吗？
Is that your name?

518
00:43:35,112 --> 00:43:38,206
你是一头可爱的野兽
You seem like such a nice beast.

519
00:43:39,516 --> 00:43:42,508
我真的希望你跟你的外表一样友好
Well, I certainly hope you are what you seem to be.

520
00:43:44,521 --> 00:43:47,319
坚持一下 我放你下来
Just hang on. I'll get you down.

521
00:43:49,126 --> 00:43:50,593
就好了
Just a second.

522
00:43:51,862 --> 00:43:53,489
对不起！
I'm sorry!

523
00:43:55,833 --> 00:43:58,131
鲁德 你受伤了吗？
Ludo, are you hurt?

524
00:44:05,943 --> 00:44:07,035
朋友？
Friend?

525
00:44:07,144 --> 00:44:09,635
是的 鲁德
That's right, Ludo.

526
00:44:09,747 --> 00:44:11,146
我是莎拉
I'm Sarah.

527
00:44:12,549 --> 00:44:13,982
莎拉
Sarah.

528
00:44:16,153 --> 00:44:18,280
起来吧 我帮你
Here, let me help you.

529
00:44:18,355 --> 00:44:20,289
你还好吗？
Are you okay?

530
00:44:26,363 --> 00:44:29,355
莎拉是朋友
Sarah friend.

531
00:44:29,399 --> 00:44:31,890
等一等
Now, wait. Just a second.

532
00:44:31,969 --> 00:44:35,735
- 我想问你一些东西 鲁德  - 什么？
- I want to ask you something, Ludo. - What?

533
00:44:35,806 --> 00:44:39,401
