00:59:14,772 --> 00:59:19,368
这个高贵的武士 让我透不过气
Yet this noble knight has fought me to a standstill.

714
00:59:19,477 --> 00:59:23,004
- 你没事吧 鲁德？  - 臭！
- Are you all right, Ludo? - Smell!

715
00:59:23,081 --> 00:59:27,211
原来你叫鲁德 我是迪迪莫斯 我服输了
Sir Ludo, if that's thy name, now I, Sir Didymus, yield to thee.

716
00:59:27,285 --> 00:59:30,220
来 让我们从此做兄弟吧…
Come, let us be brothers henceforth...

717
00:59:30,288 --> 00:59:32,916
为正义共同作战！
and fight for the right as one!

718
00:59:34,926 --> 00:59:38,327
- 非常谢谢你  - 鲁德有兄弟了
- Thank you very much. - Ludo get brother.

719
00:59:38,396 --> 00:59:39,488
一言为定
Steady.

720
00:59:40,732 --> 00:59:43,257
- 很高兴认识你 鲁德  - 太好了 来吧
- Well met, Sir Ludo. - Good. Come on.

721
00:59:43,334 --> 00:59:46,826
等等！你忘了我的誓言 小姐
Wait a minute! You forget my sacred vow, my lady.

722
00:59:46,905 --> 00:59:50,705
- 我不能让你过去  - 但是你说鲁德是你的兄弟
- I cannot let you pass. - But you said Ludo is your brother.

723
00:59:50,808 --> 00:59:54,209
我曾立誓 要誓死捍卫它
I have taken an oath, and I must defend it to the death.

724
00:59:54,312 --> 00:59:57,008
- 很臭！  - 那好
- The smell! - Okay.

725
00:59:57,115 --> 01:00:00,573
我们冷静下来想想 你到底发了什么誓？
Let's handle this thing logically. What exactly have you sworn?

726
01:00:00,652 --> 01:00:04,748
我以血发誓 如果没有我的允许…
I have sworn with my lifeblood no one shall pass this way...

727
01:00:04,822 --> 01:00:07,086
任何人都不准过桥
without my permission.

728
01:00:09,260 --> 01:00:12,593
那么我们可以得到你的允许吗？
Well, may we have your permission?

729
01:00:13,765 --> 01:00:15,198
这个我…
Well, l...

730
01:00:24,142 --> 01:00:26,201
- 好吧  - 谢谢你 你太好了
- Yes. - Thank you, noble sir.

731
01:00:26,277 --> 01:00:27,642
不用谢
My lady.

732
01:00:31,282 --> 01:00:34,251
- 噢  - 不要怕 小姐
- Uh-oh. - Have no fear, sweet lady.

733
01:00:34,352 --> 01:00:36,650
这座桥有一千年历史了
This bridge has lasted for a thousand years.

734
01:00:47,265 --> 01:00:49,290
- 看来还很坚固  - 霍格！
- It seemed solid enough. - Hoggle!

735
01:00:53,571 --> 01:00:56,233
不用怕 可爱的小姐 我来救你
Fear not, fair maiden. I will save thee.

736
01:00:56,307 --> 01:00:57,331
怎么回事
Somehow.

737
01:00:59,477 --> 01:01:03,538
鲁德 你不去救人 反而在这里大声吼叫？
Sir Ludo, canst thou sit by and howl when yon maiden needs our help?

738
01:01:33,511 --> 01:01:36,241
- 太不可思议了 鲁德  - 兄弟！
- That's incredible, Ludo. - My brother!

739
01:01:36,314 --> 01:01:38,612
你能聚集石头？
Canst thou summon up the very rocks?

740
01:01:38,716 --> 01:01:42,777
当然石头是朋友
Sure. Rocks friends.

741
01:01:47,925 --> 01:01:50,519
- 上来吧  - 谢谢你 霍格
- Here. - Thanks, Hoggle.

742
01:01:54,532 --> 01:01:56,466
小心 鲁德
Be careful, Ludo.

743
01:02:03,374 --> 01:02:05,706
等等我
Wait for me.

744
01:02:05,777 --> 01:02:10,043
安伯希斯 没事了 出来吧
Ambrosious, it's all right. You can come out now.

745
01:02:10,148 --> 01:02:13,675
来吧 好家伙
Come on. That-a boy.

746
01:02:13,751 --> 01:02:16,584
我忠心的战马来吧
My loyal steed. Steady.

747
01:02:19,757 --> 01:02:22,783
前进
Forward. Steady, boy.

748
01:02:22,860 --> 01:02:26,352
来吧 安伯希斯 闭上眼睛直走
Come on, Ambrosious. Just close your eyes and go.

749
01:02:30,168 --> 01:02:32,068
我们走吧
Let's get out of here.

750
01:02:35,873 --> 01:02:37,773
让一让 谢谢
Excuse us. Thank you.

751
01:02:44,382 --> 01:02:47,180
如果我是你 我不会那样做
<i>I wouldn't do that, if I were you.</i>

752
01:02:47,285 --> 01:02:50,743
不要逼我 我不能拿给她
Oh, please, I can't give it to her.

753
01:02:54,292 --> 01:02:58,023
走吧 我们在天黑前应该能到达城堡
Come on then. We should reach the castle well before day.

754
01:03:05,002 --> 01:03:08,403
看 莎拉 这就是你要找的东西吗？
Look, Sarah, is this what you're trying to find?

755
01:03:10,942 --> 01:03:14,605
这个小家伙多麻烦啊 但是很快就不会了
So much trouble over such a little thing, but not for long.

756
01:03:14,712 --> 01:03:19,149
她很快会忘记你 我的宝贝
She'll soon forget all about you, my fine fellow.

757
01:03:19,217 --> 01:03:22,345
只要霍格把我的礼物给她…
Just as soon as Hoggle gives her my present...

758
01:03:22,420 --> 01:03:25,617
她就会忘掉所有的东西
then she'll forget everything.

759
01:03:27,325 --> 01:03:30,226
是我的肚子还是你的 安伯希斯？
Is that my stomach or yours, Ambrosious?

760
01:03:31,529 --> 01:03:32,962
饿了
Hungry.

761
01:03:34,132 --> 01:03:38,535
是啊 但我们不能停下
Yeah. Well, we can't stop now.

762
01:03:38,636 --> 01:03:41,537
或许我们能找到野果吃
Maybe we can find some berries or something.

763
01:03:44,275 --> 01:03:46,334
干嘛？
Yeah?

764
01:03:46,477 --> 01:03:47,637
给你
Here.

765
01:03:50,481 --> 01:03:52,574
谢谢！
Thank you!

766
01:03:52,650 --> 01:03:54,777
你真是救命恩人
You're a lifesaver.

767
01:04:04,162 --> 01:04:05,754
味道很奇怪
This tastes strange.

768
01:04:14,205 --> 01:04:15,467
你放了什么？
What have you done?

769
01:04:15,573 --> 01:04:18,872
噢 该死的佳拉斯
Oh, damn you, Jareth.

770
01:04:18,976 --> 01:04:21,376
我真该死
And damn me too.

771
01:04:32,790 --> 01:04:34,724
一切都在跳动
Everything's dancing.

772
01:05:39,290 --> 01:05:43,090
太好了 停哇 安伯希斯 哇！
Yea, verily. Whoa, Ambrosious, whoa!

773
01:05:43,160 --> 01:05:47,460
城堡就在那边 小姐
The castle doth lie yonder, my lady.

774
01:05:47,565 --> 01:05:49,465
小姐？
My lady?

775
01:05:49,192 --> 01:05:51,109
小姐？
My lady?

776
01:05:51,278 --> 01:05:55,032
小姐？小姐？
My lady? My lady?

777
01:06:35,000 --> 01:06:38,000
[DAVID BOWIE - AS THE WORLD FALLS DOWN

778
01:09:45,002 --> 01:09:49,029
噢她不会原谅我
Oh, she'll never forgive me.

779
01:09:49,106 --> 01:09:51,199
我做了什么？
What have I done?

780
01:09:51,308 --> 01:09:54,277
我失去了唯一的朋友
I've lost my only friend.

781
01:09:54,345 --> 01:09:56,438
我失去了朋友
That's what I've done.

782
01:10:06,957 --> 01:10:08,925
我刚才在干什么？
What was I doing?

783
01:10:20,971 --> 01:10:22,939
下来！
Get off my back!

784
01:10:25,442 --> 01:10:28,002
干嘛不想想你要去哪里…
Why don't you look where you're going...

785
01:10:28,078 --> 01:10:30,046
小女孩 啊？
young woman, hmm?

786
01:10:31,382 --> 01:10:34,545
- 我在找呢  - 哈？哈？
- I was looking. - Huh? Huh?

787
01:10:34,652 --> 01:10:37,644
你打算去哪里啊？
Where were you going, hmm?

788
01:10:37,755 --> 01:10:39,484
我忘记了
I don't remember.

789
01:10:39,557 --> 01:10:42,822
你不知道要去哪里 找也没用
You can't look where you're going if you don't know where you're going.

790
01:10:42,893 --> 01:10:44,554
我在找东西
I was searching for something.

791
01:10:45,462 --> 01:10:47,020
看看
Look here.

792
01:10:51,969 --> 01:10:53,368
兰斯洛特？
Lancelot?

793
01:10:55,406 --> 01:10:56,498
谢谢
Thank you.

794
01:10:56,574 --> 01:11:01,068
这就是你要找的 是吗亲爱的？
That's what you were looking for, wasn't it, my dear?

795
01:11:01,178 --> 01:11:04,272
是的 我刚才忘了
Yes. I forgot.

796
01:11:04,381 --> 01:11:07,373
那么你为什么…
Now, why don't you...

797
01:11:07,484 --> 01:11:09,679
不进来…
come in here...

798
01:11:09,787 --> 01:11:12,688
看看还有没有其它东西…
and see if there's anything else...

799
01:11:12,790 --> 01:11:15,088
你喜欢的啊？
you'd like, hmm?

800
01:11:45,556 --> 01:11:47,615
只是一个梦
It was just a dream.

801
01:11:50,327 --> 01:11:52,887
我做了个梦 兰斯洛特
I dreamed it all, Lancelot.

802
01:11:55,165 --> 01:11:57,224
但是很真实
But it was so real.

803
01:12:00,437 --> 01:12:03,031
去看看爸爸回来没有 好吗？
Let's go see if Daddy's back, okay?

804
01:12:08,278 --> 01:12:10,746
最好留在这里 亲爱的
Better to stay in here, dear. Yes.

805
01:12:10,848 --> 01:12:15,251
外面没有你要的东西 没有！
There's nothing you want out there. No!

806
01:12:15,352 --> 01:12:18,253
看看这里有什么？
Oh, what have we got here?

807
01:12:18,355 --> 01:12:19,754
兰斯洛特
Lancelot.

808
01:12:20,858 --> 01:12:23,326
你可爱的小兔子 你喜欢可爱的小兔子
Your little bunny rabbit. You like your little bunny rabbit.

809
01:12:23,394 --> 01:12:25,794
不是吗？ 是的 是的 给你
Don't you? Yes, yes. There you go.

810
01:12:25,863 --> 01:12:28,354
还有小人偶 你记得小人偶 是吗？
There's Betsy Bou. You remember Betsy Bou, don't you?

811
01:12:28,465 --> 01:12:30,262
对对
Yes, yes.

812
01:12:30,367 --> 01:12:33,768
那么我们还有什么？ 这是什么？我们看看
Now, then, what else have we got? What's this? Let's have a look.

813
01:12:33,871 --> 01:12:36,431
是个铅笔盒 里面还有很多铅笔
It's a pencil box. Got lots of pencils in it too.

814
01:12:37,875 --> 01:12:41,003
这是你的熊猫拖鞋 你很喜欢它们的
Here's your panda slippers. You know how much you like them.

815
01:12:41,078 --> 01:12:44,605
你不想它们被扔掉吧 给你 很好
You never wanted them thrown away. There they are. That's right.

816
01:12:44,682 --> 01:12:48,413
现在还有什么？ 噢 一只小马
Okay, now then, what else? Oh, it's little Horsey.

817
01:12:48,485 --> 01:12:50,919
你喜欢小马 不是吗 亲爱的？
You love little Horsey, don't you, dear?

818
01:12:50,988 --> 01:12:55,084
看看这个！ 你有画画游戏 给你
And look at this! You got a printing game, you have.

819
01:12:55,192 --> 01:12:58,855
这是宝物 你喜欢 对不对 亲爱的？
Oh, here's a treasure. You'll want that, won't you, my dear?

820
01:12:58,929 --> 01:13:02,797
好的 试一下 化化妆
Yes, go on, put it on. Make yourself up.

821
01:13:02,833 --> 01:13:06,291
这是可爱的弗罗茜 你喜欢 给你
Here's dear old Flopsy. You'll want her. There you go.

822
01:13:07,104 --> 01:13:10,301
对了 对了
Oh, yes. Ah, oh, yes.

823
01:13:10,407 --> 01:13:14,207
查理熊 好的 给你小熊
Charlie Bear. Right. There's Charlie Bear for you.

824
01:13:14,244 --> 01:13:16,212
我在找一些东西
There was something I was looking for.

825
01:13:16,246 --> 01:13:18,714
啊 别乱说
Ah, don't talk nonsense.

826
01:13:18,816 --> 01:13:23,879
都在这里了 你要的都在这里了
It's all here. Everything you've ever cared about is all right here.

827
01:13:23,954 --> 01:13:26,354
这是你的糖果店玩具
There's your little toy candy shop.

828
01:13:26,423 --> 01:13:27,788
“经历数之不尽的艰难…
"Through dangers untold...

829
01:13:27,858 --> 01:13:30,622
和无尽的险阻…
and hardships unnumbered...

830
01:13:31,662 --> 01:13:35,120
我终于到了去城堡的路…
I fought my way here to the castle...

831
01:13:35,165 --> 01:13:37,793
要穿越格布林鬼城…
beyond the Goblin City...

832
01:13:37,868 --> 01:13:41,201
找回被你偷走的小孩”
to take back the child that you have stolen. "

833
01:13:42,573 --> 01:13:46,168
怎么了 亲爱的？ 不喜欢你的玩具吗？
What's the matter, my dear? Don't you like your toys?

834
01:13:47,244 --> 01:13:48,336
这些都是废物
It's all junk.

835
01:13:49,980 --> 01:13:52,210
那么这个呢？
Well, what about this?

836
01:13:52,282 --> 01:13:56,184
这个不是废物吧？
This is not junk, eh?

837
01:13:57,154 --> 01:13:59,554
这是！
Yes, it is!

838
01:14:00,591 --> 01:14:03,355
我要去救托比！
I have to save Toby!

839
01:14:07,698 --> 01:14:09,131
小姐！
My lady!

840
01:14:11,468 --> 01:14:13,402
你没事吧？
Are you all right?

841
01:14:20,177 --> 01:14:22,805
美丽的小姐 你没事真是太好了
Fair maiden. Thank goodness thou art safe at last.

842
01:14:22,880 --> 01:14:25,110
