- Where are we? - Sarah back.

843
01:14:25,182 --> 01:14:27,616
小姐 我们就快到了
My lady, we're almost there.

844
01:14:27,684 --> 01:14:30,175
那是格布林鬼城的门
Those are the gates to the Goblin City.

845
01:14:30,220 --> 01:14:32,381
鲁德 迪迪莫斯
Ludo, Sir Didymus.

846
01:14:33,991 --> 01:14:36,221
赶快走吧 时间不多了
Let's go quickly. We don't have much time.

847
01:14:36,293 --> 01:14:38,625
- 好  - 好吧 安伯希斯
- Yeah. - Right, Ambrosious.

848
01:14:38,695 --> 01:14:40,686
前进
Forward.

849
01:14:40,798 --> 01:14:42,197
去吧
You know.

850
01:14:45,435 --> 01:14:47,665
开门 打开门
Open up. Open the door.

851
01:14:47,738 --> 01:14:49,899
迪迪莫斯 我们得悄悄进去
Sir Didymus, we must go quietly.

852
01:14:52,042 --> 01:14:54,010
开门 赶快开门！
Open up. Open up right now!

853
01:14:54,044 --> 01:14:55,534
你会吵醒守卫
You'll wake the guard.

854
01:14:55,612 --> 01:14:56,943
安静
Quiet.

855
01:14:57,014 --> 01:14:59,778
来吧 把他们全吵醒！
Well, let them all wake up!

856
01:15:00,818 --> 01:15:03,844
我要把你们全杀死！
I shall fight you all to the death!

857
01:15:05,923 --> 01:15:09,324
拜托 迪迪莫斯 我求你安静下来
Please, Sir Didymus, for my sake, hush.

858
01:15:09,359 --> 01:15:11,486
当然可以 为了你 什么都可以
But of course. For thee, anything.

859
01:15:11,562 --> 01:15:13,928
- 但我不是懦夫？  - 对
- But I'm not a coward? - No.

860
01:15:14,031 --> 01:15:16,158
- 我的嗅觉很灵敏？  - 是的
- And my sense of smell is keen? - Oh, yes.

861
01:15:16,233 --> 01:15:19,862
那么我就可以随时随地战斗！
Then I shall fight anyone anywhere, anyplace, any time!

862
01:15:19,937 --> 01:15:21,768
我们知道！
We know!

863
01:15:21,839 --> 01:15:23,272
安静下来
Now hush.

864
01:15:25,242 --> 01:15:27,335
安静
Quietly.

865
01:15:27,444 --> 01:15:29,844
安伯希斯 安静
Ambrosious, be quiet now.

866
01:15:31,281 --> 01:15:33,511
我不明白为什么要安静
I don't see why we have to be so quiet.

867
01:15:33,584 --> 01:15:35,779
只是一个格布林鬼城而已
It's only a Goblin City.

868
01:15:35,853 --> 01:15:37,787
我感觉有麻烦了
I smell trouble.

869
01:15:43,594 --> 01:15:45,027
小心 鲁德
Come on, Ludo.

870
01:15:46,363 --> 01:15:47,762
不
Oh, no.

871
01:15:51,668 --> 01:15:53,568
那是什么？
What is that?

872
01:15:57,674 --> 01:15:59,767
谁想过去？
Who goes?

873
01:16:05,382 --> 01:16:07,213
谁想过去？
Who goes?

874
01:16:22,532 --> 01:16:24,159
小心！
Watch out!

875
01:16:38,015 --> 01:16:40,108
安伯希斯 过来好吗？
Ambrosious, will you come here?

876
01:16:43,921 --> 01:16:45,047
马上过来！
Come here right now!

877
01:16:45,923 --> 01:16:48,517
请你过来好吗？你让我很难堪
Will you please come into the open? You're embarrassing me.

878
01:17:03,340 --> 01:17:05,365
小心！
Look out!

879
01:17:07,678 --> 01:17:09,703
走吧
Get out of there.

880
01:17:10,981 --> 01:17:12,949
你想干嘛？
What are you doing?

881
01:17:14,451 --> 01:17:16,351
走开！
Bombs away!

882
01:17:19,856 --> 01:17:21,881
不是很好
That wasn't very nice.

883
01:17:23,694 --> 01:17:24,888
轮到我了
My turn now.

884
01:17:26,663 --> 01:17:28,858
怎么驾驶？
How do you drive this thing?

885
01:17:32,602 --> 01:17:34,729
扔掉斧头！
Drop the ax!

886
01:17:34,805 --> 01:17:37,103
我在想办法
I'm trying.

887
01:17:37,174 --> 01:17:40,234
下来吧
Come here at once.

888
01:17:40,310 --> 01:17:42,574
发生什么事？
What's happened?

889
01:17:42,679 --> 01:17:44,579
哪一个是后退？
Where's reverse?

890
01:17:51,588 --> 01:17:54,682
离开那儿 霍格！
Get out of there, Hoggle!

891
01:17:54,791 --> 01:17:56,486
弃船
Abandon ship.

892
01:18:05,135 --> 01:18:07,330
霍格 你没事吧？
Hoggle, are you all right?

893
01:18:08,505 --> 01:18:12,168
我不奢望你的原谅 我不为自己的所作所为感到内疚
I'm not asking to be forgiven. I ain't ashamed of nothin' I did.

894
01:18:12,242 --> 01:18:15,734
佳拉斯叫我把桃子给你
Jareth made me give you that peach.

895
01:18:15,812 --> 01:18:19,441
我不介意你怎么看我 我说过我是懦夫
I don't care what you think of me. I told you I was a coward.

896
01:18:19,516 --> 01:18:21,507
我想和你做朋友
I ain't interested in being friends.

897
01:18:22,953 --> 01:18:24,352
我原谅你
I forgive you.

898
01:18:25,922 --> 01:18:28,152
你…真的吗？
You... You do?

899
01:18:29,426 --> 01:18:33,089
我要称赞你 你的勇气可嘉
And I commend you. Rarely have I seen such courage.

900
01:18:33,163 --> 01:18:36,462
你是一个勇敢的人 霍格
You are a valiant man, Sir Hoggle.

901
01:18:36,533 --> 01:18:39,195
- 是吗？  - 是的
- I am? - Yeah.

902
01:18:39,269 --> 01:18:41,737
霍格和鲁德是朋友
Hoggle and Ludo friends.

903
01:18:43,040 --> 01:18:45,474
- 真的吗？  - 真的
- We are? - Yeah.

904
01:18:45,542 --> 01:18:47,066
这是你的东西
Here are your things.

905
01:18:48,545 --> 01:18:49,705
谢谢你帮忙
Thanks for your help.

906
01:18:49,780 --> 01:18:53,272
那么我们还等什么？
Well, what are we waiting for?

907
01:18:53,350 --> 01:18:55,875
一起把那个叫佳拉斯的老鼠抓出来
Let's get the rat who calls himself Jareth.

908
01:18:55,952 --> 01:18:57,476
好走吧
Right. Come on.

909
01:18:57,554 --> 01:19:00,489
安伯希斯 现在安全了 不要怕
Ambrosious, it's safe now. Nothing to be afraid of.

910
01:19:26,283 --> 01:19:28,478
陛下！
Your Highness!

911
01:19:30,587 --> 01:19:33,579
- 陛下 那个女孩…  - 什么？
- Your Highness, the girl... - What?

912
01:19:33,690 --> 01:19:36,989
吃了桃子 忘记了所有事的  - 她怎么了？
- Who ate the peach, forgot everything. - What of her?

913
01:19:37,094 --> 01:19:40,222
她和一只妖怪来了 还有你手下的迪迪莫斯和侏儒
She's here with the monster and Sir Didymus and the dwarf who works for you.

914
01:19:40,297 --> 01:19:43,289
- 什么？  - 他们朝城堡这边来了！
- What? - They're on their way to the castle!

915
01:19:43,333 --> 01:19:47,326
阻止她！叫守卫来 把婴儿藏起来
Stop her! Call out the guards. Take the baby and hide it.

916
01:19:47,404 --> 01:19:48,496
守卫！
Guards!

917
01:19:48,605 --> 01:19:51,574
必须阻止她 赶快！
She must be stopped. Do something!

918
01:19:52,509 --> 01:19:55,672
快行动 行动！
Come on, move. Move!

919
01:20:04,821 --> 01:20:08,416
- 我想我们就快到了  - 哈 小菜一碟
- I think we're gonna make it. - Oh, piece of cake.

920
01:20:15,031 --> 01:20:18,057
大伙停
Company, halt.

921
01:20:24,674 --> 01:20:27,643
长矛准备！
Lances ready!

922
01:20:30,847 --> 01:20:32,815
大炮发射！
Cannon, fire!

923
01:20:38,788 --> 01:20:41,621
安伯希斯 掉头 掉头
Ambrosious, turn around. Turn about.

924
01:20:41,691 --> 01:20:44,421
- 快 这边  - 好吧 冲！
- Quick, this way. - All right. Charge!

925
01:20:46,062 --> 01:20:48,053
不 不是那边！
No, not that way!

926
01:20:49,866 --> 01:20:53,267
你走错了！
You're going the wrong way!

927
01:20:53,370 --> 01:20:55,270
敌人在我们后面！
The battle's behind us!

928
01:20:59,209 --> 01:21:03,077
安伯希斯 我们谈谈好吗？
Ambrosious, can we please talk about this?

929
01:21:03,113 --> 01:21:04,546
停！
Sit!

930
01:21:09,085 --> 01:21:11,610
小心点 好吗
Be careful. Okay.

931
01:21:11,688 --> 01:21:13,121
这边
Through here.

932
01:21:15,926 --> 01:21:19,555
安伯希斯 站住
Ambrosious, stand still.

933
01:21:20,497 --> 01:21:22,431
好吧来吧
Okay, come on, guys.

934
01:21:23,934 --> 01:21:26,767
安伯希斯 如果你再不掉头…
Ambrosious, if you don't turn around this second...

935
01:21:26,836 --> 01:21:29,634
我就不喂你了
I will never feed you again.

936
01:21:31,908 --> 01:21:33,341
这还差不多
That's better.

937
01:21:35,111 --> 01:21:37,944
别担心 安伯希斯 我想我们被包围了
Don't worry, Ambrosious. I think we've got them surrounded.

938
01:21:41,017 --> 01:21:43,645
迪迪莫斯！ 迪迪莫斯在哪里？
Didymus! Where's Didymus?

939
01:21:43,720 --> 01:21:46,154
开火！
Fire!

940
01:21:48,225 --> 01:21:50,159
我打中了吗？有没有？
I hit something, yes? No?

941
01:21:51,561 --> 01:21:54,029
我们要找到迪迪莫斯
We've got to find Didymus.

942
01:21:55,565 --> 01:21:57,897
这边
Down this way.

943
01:22:15,252 --> 01:22:18,153
冲啊！
Charge!

944
01:22:25,562 --> 01:22:26,995
呔嗬！
Tallyho!

945
01:22:31,101 --> 01:22:33,433
安伯希斯 你这个懦夫
Ambrosious, you coward.

946
01:22:43,480 --> 01:22:45,880
快进去
Quick, in here.

947
01:22:45,982 --> 01:22:47,779
鲁德怎么进来？
How's Ludo gonna get in?

948
01:23:09,539 --> 01:23:11,632
你们被包围了！
You in there, you're surrounded!

949
01:23:12,509 --> 01:23:14,238
包围？
Surrounded?

950
01:23:16,112 --> 01:23:19,377
出去！鲁德 守住屋顶！
Get out! Ludo, hold the roof!

951
01:23:30,760 --> 01:23:32,921
- 接招！  - 饿了吗？
- Take that! - Hungry?

952
01:23:38,234 --> 01:23:41,135
安伯希斯 开门
Ambrosious, unlock this door.

953
01:23:46,976 --> 01:23:49,501
玩够了吗？
So, had enough, have you?

954
01:23:49,579 --> 01:23:54,175
放下你们的武器 我会让你们好受点
Then throw down your weapons, and I'll see that you're well-treated.

955
01:24:21,778 --> 01:24:23,712
下次再投降吧
Next time, surrender.

956
01:24:33,390 --> 01:24:35,551
做的好！
Good grief!

957
01:24:40,730 --> 01:24:41,822
停下
Steady, men.

958
01:24:44,601 --> 01:24:46,694
停 不要动
Steady, men. Hold your ground.

959
01:24:51,508 --> 01:24:54,500
当我没说 逃命吧！
Okay, I take it back. Run for your lives!

960
01:24:54,611 --> 01:24:57,774
我受够了！我要睡觉
I've had enough! I'm going to bed.

961
01:25:00,016 --> 01:25:01,984
出去！
Get out of my house!

962
01:25:24,140 --> 01:25:26,404
哇 内尔！闪开！
Whoa, Nellie! Duck!

963
01:25:29,446 --> 01:25:30,777
偏了！
Missed!

964
01:25:30,847 --> 01:25:32,644
好来吧
Okay, come on.

965
01:25:35,151 --> 01:25:36,584
开火！
Fire!

966
01:25:39,055 --> 01:25:41,148
喂 我开火了
Hey, I just fired you.

967
01:25:41,257 --> 01:25:43,054
唉唷 哎唷 哎唷！
Ouch, ouch, ouch!

968
01:25:45,962 --> 01:25:47,361
这边
This way.

969
01:25:51,801 --> 01:25:52,893
我们抓到你们了！
Now we have you!

970
01:25:55,104 --> 01:25:56,537
现在抓不到了
And now you don't.

971
01:26:13,990 --> 01:26:16,117
没问题
Hey, no problem.

972
01:26:19,596 --> 01:26:22,258
- 迪迪莫斯！  - 来了！
- Sir Didymus! - Coming!

973
01:26:24,601 --> 01:26:27,229
嘿哟 银牌！
Hi-ho, Silver!

974
01:26:37,847 --> 01:26:40,816
- 哇 好家伙 哇太棒了  - 这边
- Whoa, boy. Whoa, big fella. - This way.

975
01:26:40,917 --> 01:26:42,316
停
Steady, boy.

976
01:26:44,254 --> 01:26:47,553
好 上去 上
Ah, yes. Up we go. Up, up.

977
01:26:49,859 --> 01:26:51,827
来吧 好样的
Come on. Good boy.

978
01:26:51,861 --> 01:26:53,829
来
Come on.

979
01:26:53,863 --> 01:26:55,160
不
No.

980
01:26:55,231 --> 01:26:57,096
好 走吧
Good boy. Come on.

981
01:26:58,535 --> 01:27:01,698
- 他只有这条路走了  - 那么 走吧
- That's the only way he could have gone. - Well, then, come on.

982
01:27:01,771 --> 01:27:05,229
- 我必须自己去找他  - 为什么？
- I have to face him alone. - But why?

983
01:27:05,275 --> 01:27:07,402
因为开始时就是这样
Because that's the way it's done.

984
01:27:07,477 --> 01:27:10,037
好吧 如果开始是这样…
Well, if that is the way it is done...

985
01:27:10,146 --> 01:27:12,376
你就必须这样去做
then that is the way you must do it.

986
01:27:12,448 --> 01:27:15,246
但是如果你需要帮忙…
But should you need us...

987
01:27:16,185 --> 01:27:18,483
是的 如果需要帮忙…
Yes, should you need us...

988
01:27:19,656 --> 01:27:21,021
我会叫你们
I'll call.

989
01:27:22,091 --> 01:27:23,956
谢谢 谢谢你们
Thank you, all of you.

990
01:28:46,142 --> 01:28:47,905
托比！
Toby!

991
01:29:53,409 --> 01:29:55,809
托比！
Toby!

992
01:30:56,773 --> 01:30:58,707
把孩子给我
Give me the child.

993
01:30:58,775 --> 01:31:01,107
莎拉 小心了
Sarah, beware.

994
01:31:01,177 --> 01:31:05,409
直到现在我都很仁慈 我也可以残忍
I have been generous up until now, and I can be cruel.

995
01:31:05,481 --> 01:31:06,914
仁慈？
Generous?

996
01:31:09,118 --> 01:31:12,451
- 你做了什么叫仁慈？  - 一切！
- What have you done that's generous? - Everything!

997
01:31:12,522 --> 01:31:15,491
你要的一切我都做了
Everything that you have wanted, I have done.

998
01:31:15,525 --> 01:31:19,484
你要我把小孩带走 我做了
You asked that the child be taken. I took him.

999
01:31:19,529 --> 01:31:22,828
你在我面前退缩 我很可怕
You cowered before me. I was frightening.

1000
01:31:22,899 --> 01:31:25,265
我重新定了时间
I have reordered time.

1001
01:31:25,334 --> 01:31:28,064
我把世界倒转…
I have turned the world upside-down...

1002
01:31:28,137 --> 01:31:30,731
这一切都是为了你
and I have done it all for you.

1003
01:31:32,341 --> 01:31:36,334
为了满足你 我身心疲倦
I am exhausted from living up to your expectations of me.

1004
01:31:36,412 --> 01:31:37,606
这还不算仁慈吗？
Isn't that generous?

1005
01:31:41,150 --> 01:31:44,415
经历数之不尽的艰难险阻…
Through dangers untold and hardships unnumbered...

1006
01:31:45,922 --> 01:31:49,756
我终于到了城堡 在格布林鬼城那里
I have fought my way here to the castle beyond the Goblin City.

1007
01:31:52,461 --> 01:31:54,429
因为我的毅力同你一样坚韧…
For my will is as strong as yours...

1008
01:31:55,665 --> 01:31:58,691
- 我的…  - 停止 等一等
- and my... - Stop. Wait.

1009
01:31:58,768 --> 01:32:00,395
看 莎拉
Look, Sarah.

1010
01:32:00,469 --> 01:32:04,166
看我给你什么
Look what I'm offering you.

1011
01:32:04,240 --> 01:32:05,730
你的梦想
Your dreams.

1012
01:32:07,944 --> 01:32:10,504
我的国度一样的伟大…
And my kingdom as great...

1013
01:32:10,580 --> 01:32:13,413
我只有小小的要求
I ask for so little.

1014
01:32:13,482 --> 01:32:16,007
让我控制你…
Just let me rule you...

1015
01:32:16,085 --> 01:32:19,543
你就能得到你想要的一切
and you can have everything that you want.

1016
01:32:22,258 --> 01:32:25,750
国度一样的伟大？
Kingdom as great?

1017
01:32:25,862 --> 01:32:27,159
该死的
Damn.

1018
01:32:27,263 --> 01:32:29,493
我怎么也记不住这一行
I can never remember that line.

1019
01:32:29,565 --> 01:32:33,365
只要你敬畏我 爱我 听我的话…
Just fear me, love me, do as I say...

1020
01:32:33,469 --> 01:32:35,869
我可以成为你的奴隶
and I will be your slave.

1021
01:32:36,873 --> 01:32:40,969
我的国度一样的伟大… 我的国度一样的伟大…
My kingdom as great... My kingdom as great...

1022
01:32:47,683 --> 01:32:50,151
你的法力并不强过我
You have no power over me.

1023
01:32:51,988 --> 01:32:54,957
你的法力并不强过我
You have no power over me.

1024
01:33:38,768 --> 01:33:40,201
托比
Toby.

1025
01:34:15,571 --> 01:34:18,369
给你
Here you are.

1026
01:34:18,474 --> 01:34:21,409
我现在把兰斯洛特送给你
I'd like Lancelot to belong to you now.

1027
01:34:44,834 --> 01:34:46,267
我们回来了
We're home.

1028
01:34:53,042 --> 01:34:55,101
莎拉 你在家吗？
Sarah, are you home?

1029
01:34:56,212 --> 01:34:58,442
在 我在家
Yeah. Yes, I'm home.

1030
01:35:01,617 --> 01:35:03,551
再见莎拉
Good-bye, Sarah.

1031
01:35:13,229 --> 01:35:14,753
记住 美丽的小姐…
Remember, fair maiden...

1032
01:35:14,830 --> 01:35:16,764
如果你需要我们…
should you need us...

1033
01:35:17,967 --> 01:35:20,197
对 如果你需要我们…
Yes, should you need us...

1034
01:35:20,269 --> 01:35:23,170
无论什么原因…
for any reason at all...

1035
01:35:23,239 --> 01:35:25,730
我需要你 霍格
I need you, Hoggle.

1036
01:35:25,775 --> 01:35:27,208
真的？
You do?

1037
01:35:28,544 --> 01:35:31,035
不知道为什么 但是…
I don't know why, but...

1038
01:35:31,147 --> 01:35:33,707
无论现在还是将来…
every now and again in my life...

1039
01:35:33,783 --> 01:35:37,150
不为任何原因 我需要你
for no reason at all, I need you.

1040
01:35:37,253 --> 01:35:39,153
需要你们大家
All of you.

1041
01:35:39,255 --> 01:35:40,916
真的？
You do?

1042
01:35:40,990 --> 01:35:44,323
为什么不早说呢？
Well, why didn't you say so?

1043
01:35:55,704 --> 01:35:57,865
- 噢 鲁德！  - 莎拉
- Oh, Ludo! - Sarah.

1044
01:35:57,973 --> 01:36:01,534
安伯希斯 好家伙
Ambrosious, good boy, good boy.

1045
01:36:08,584 --> 01:36:11,178
我说 有人想玩拼字游戏吗？
I say, does anyone here want to play a game of Scrabble?


